text: Pogonocherus eugeniae is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Ganglbauer in 1891. It is known from Croatia, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Austria, Greece, Romania, and Italy.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus eugeniae.
